<sentence type="quasi">松本サリン</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告に懲役<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t1" type="DURATION" value="P17Y" valueFromSurface="P17Y">１７年</TIMEX3></sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">東京高裁一審支持<quote>「役割は<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e1">従属的</EVENT>」</quote></sentence>
<sentence>　松本サリン事件の実行役として殺人、殺人未遂罪などに<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e2">問われた</EVENT>教団元信者、<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t2" type="DURATION" value="P43Y" valueFromSurface="P43Y">四三</TIMEX3>）の控訴審判決公判が<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t3" type="DATE" value="2001-08-31" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-31">三十一日</TIMEX3>、東京高裁で<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e3">開かれ</EVENT>、<sampling type="start" />金山薫裁判長は<quote>「被告の刑事責任は<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e4">重大だ</EVENT>が、<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e5">果たした</EVENT>役割は<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e6">従属的</EVENT>」</quote>などと<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e7">し</EVENT>て、懲役<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t4" type="DURATION" value="P17Y" valueFromSurface="P17Y">十七年</TIMEX3>を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e8">言い渡した</EVENT>一審・東京地裁判決を支持、検察側、<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告側双方の控訴を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e9">棄却した</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>同事件の実行犯に対し、控訴審判決が<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e10">出た</EVENT>のは初めて。</sentence>
<sentence>　判決によると、<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告は<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告＝公判中＝らと<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e11">共謀し</EVENT>、<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t5" type="TIME" value="1994-06-27TDW" valueFromSurface="H6-06-27TDW">平成六年六月二十七日未明</TIMEX3>、長野県松本市北深志の駐車場で噴霧車からサリンを<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e12">まい</EVENT>て七人を殺害、百数十人に中毒症を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e13">負わせた</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告は他の実行犯を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e14">乗せた</EVENT>ワゴン車を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e15">運転し</EVENT>て現場に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e16">同行し</EVENT>、噴霧中には犯行の妨害を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e17">防ぐ</EVENT><quote>「警護役」</quote>としてワゴン車内で周囲を警戒。</sentence>
<sentence>さらに<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t6" type="DATE" value="1994-07" valueFromSurface="H06-07">六年七月</TIMEX3>から<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t7" type="DATE" value="1994-12" valueFromSurface="H06-07">同年十二月</TIMEX3>に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e18">かけ</EVENT>て、山梨県上九一色村の教団施設のサリン量産プラントでサリンの生成に<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e19">かかわった</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e20">漂う</EVENT>秋の香り</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">マツタケ輸入ピーク</sentence>
<sentence>　マツタケの輸入量が全国消費の四割を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e21">占める</EVENT>関西国際空港で<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t8" type="DATE" value="2001-08-31" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-31">三十一日</TIMEX3>、中国産マツタケの輸入がピークを<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e22">迎え</EVENT>、関西空港税関支署では係官が通関検査に<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e23">追われた</EVENT>＝写真。</sentence>
<sentence>　<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t9" type="DATE" value="2001-08-31" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-XX">この日</TIMEX3>、関空で<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e24">通関された</EVENT>マツタケは三十五トンで、中国雲南省産が七割、残りが四川省、吉林省から空輸。</sentence>
<sentence>中国産は<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t10" type="DATE" value="2001-06" valueFromSurface="XXXX-06">六月</TIMEX3>から輸入が<EVENT class="ASPECTUAL" eid="e25">始まり</EVENT>、<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t11" type="DATE" value="2001-09" valueFromSurface="XXXX-09">九月</TIMEX3>に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e26">入る</EVENT>と、主流は韓国産に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e27">移る</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　関空経由のマツタケは関東から九州の市場に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e28">運ばれる</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>輸入業者によると<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t12" type="DATE" value="2001" valueFromSurface="XXXX">今年</TIMEX3>は色や香りも<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e29">上々で</EVENT>、<TIMEX3 definite="TRUE" tid="t13" type="DATE" value="PRESENT_REF" valueFromSurface="PRESENT_REF">現在</TIMEX3>一キロ当たり高値一万五千円程度で<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e30">取引され</EVENT>、例年より二割ほど<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e31">安い</EVENT>と<EVENT class="REPORTING" eid="e32">いう</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ミイラ騒動</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">民家の壁から赤ちゃん遺体…実は小動物</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">尼崎　警察も<quote>「大事件です奥さん」</quote></sentence>
<sentence>　エッ、ふろ場の壁の中から赤ちゃんのミイラが―。</sentence>
<sentence>兵庫県尼崎市武庫川町の機械据え付け業の男性（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t14" type="DURATION" value="P61Y" valueFromSurface="P61Y">六一</TIMEX3>）の会社兼自宅で<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t15" type="TIME" value="2001-08-31TAF" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-31TAF">三十一日午後</TIMEX3>、男性の妻（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t16" type="DURATION" value="P55Y" valueFromSurface="P55Y">五五</TIMEX3>）や警察官が、浴室の壁（厚さ約八センチ）から<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e33">見つかった</EVENT>小動物の死がいを人間の赤ちゃんと<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e34">早合点し</EVENT>、兵庫県警が一時<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e35">本格的に</EVENT>捜査に<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e36">乗り出す</EVENT>騒ぎが<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e37">あった</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　“事件発生”は、<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" mod="APPROX" tid="t17" type="TIME" value="2001-08-31T15:45" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-XXT15:45">この日午後三時四十五分ごろ</TIMEX3>。</sentence>
<sentence>妻が、改築中の浴室の壁の中から<quote>「人間の赤ちゃんのミイラのようなもの（体長約二〇センチ）を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e38">見つけた</EVENT>」</quote>と近くの交番に<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e39">通報した</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e40">駆けつけた</EVENT>県警尼崎西署員も、その場で赤ちゃんの遺体と判断。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「奥さん、大事件ですよ」</quote>と同署に無線で<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e41">連絡し</EVENT>、応援を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e42">求めた</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　周囲には近所の住民らが<quote>「何事か」</quote>と<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e43">集まり</EVENT>、上空には報道関係のヘリコプターが<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e44">旋回する</EVENT>など、一時騒然と<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e45">した</EVENT>雰囲気に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e46">包まれた</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　ところが、捜査員が<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e47">慎重に</EVENT>遺体を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e48">取り上げてみる</EVENT>と、きばとしっぽが<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e49">見つかった</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>指も人間より一本<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e50">少なかった</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence type="fragment">同署は</sentence>
<sentence>「<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e51">お騒がせしました</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">小動物でした」</sentence>
<sentence type="fragment">と、<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e52">集まった</EVENT>住民に事情を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e53">説明し</EVENT>、<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e54">一件落着した</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　調べでは、ネズミ類やイタチなどの小動物のミイラと<EVENT class="I_STATE" eid="e55">みられる</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>壁のすき間に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e56">落ち</EVENT>て、<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e57">はい上がれなく</EVENT><sampling type="end" /><EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e58">なったらしい</EVENT>。</sentence>
